flowchart TB
  U[Users / Executives / Ops] --> UI[EAOL Web & Admin UI]
  UI --> API[API Gateway]
  API --> IAM[OIDC/SAML + RBAC/ABAC]
  API --> POL[Policy & Governance]
  API --> REASON[Hybrid Reasoning Engine]
  API --> WF[Workflow Orchestration]

  subgraph Integration Fabric
    ERP[ERP]
    CRM[CRM]
    ITSM[ITSM]
    BI[BI / DWH]
    HRIS[HRIS]
    DOCS[GED / Documents]
    CONN[Connector Factory]
    BUS[Kafka Event Bus]
    NORM[Normalization Service]
  end

  ERP --> CONN
  CRM --> CONN
  ITSM --> CONN
  BI --> CONN
  HRIS --> CONN
  DOCS --> CONN
  CONN --> BUS --> NORM

  subgraph Knowledge Plane
    PG[(PostgreSQL + pgvector)]
    KG[(Neo4j Knowledge Graph)]
    OBJ[(Object Store)]
  end

  NORM --> PG
  NORM --> KG
  NORM --> OBJ

  REASON --> PG
  REASON --> KG
  REASON --> LLM[AI Provider Boundary]
  REASON --> EXPL[Explainability & Evidence]
  WF --> HITL[Human Approval]
  WF --> ACT[Approved Action Connectors]
  POL --> AUDIT[Immutable Audit]
